${offset 1}${color0}${membar 4,17}${color}${goto 32}F: ${font Liberation Sans:style=Bold:size=8}${color2}${memeasyfree}${color}${font} U: ${font Liberation Sans:style=Bold:size=8}${color2}${mem}${color}${font}
